{"type": "article", "id": 2204, "title": "桌面绿植装置 Starera", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:24:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222252p4D7dcbXlqhUxwfg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">意大利 Fabrica 工作室近日带来一款小巧精致的桌面绿植装置” Statera “，其目的是让白领一族办公室也能感受到一份绿意盎然。Statera 一词取自拉丁文，译为平衡，由一个黑色的金属架子撑起左右两边各一个陶瓷容器，坐落在一个椭圆形的石头基座上。底部的石头基座可以收纳一些桌面上的零散小物，周边的小孔还可以被当作是简易笔筒，两个陶瓷容器则是专为绿植打造的空间。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134909Ek2smIxwhuA7liWP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261349091vU3yRzwieSbQJD0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072613491084zYBGkCoT0H1nNj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}